title: Poll: Donald Trump Boasts Double-Digit Lead in Utah
description: Former President Donald Trump has a double-digit lead in the hypothetical 2024 Republican primary race in Utah, an OH Predictive Insights survey released this week found.
author: Hannah Bleau, Hannah Bleau

title: GOP Gov. Chris Sununu says Trump isn't 'bringing that fire' people saw in 2016 and predicts he won't win New Hampshire's primary

author: cpanella@insider.com (Chris Panella,Brent D. Griffiths)

title: Chris Christie says Donald Trump 'can't win a general election' and GOP is finally recognizing harm of 'loser' candidates after 2022
description: As Donald Trump claims he is "more committed now than I ever was," Chris Christie said the GOP is realizing the consequences of "loser" candidates.

title: Century-old train tunnels in Baltimore and New York to get funding from Biden's infrastructure law
description: Long-needed improvements are coming to train travel along the nation's busy Northeast Corridor, thanks in part to the federal infrastructure funding package that President Joe Biden signed into law in the fall of 2021.
author: Katie Lobosco
